text: Adriana Díaz Contreras (born 1 March 1970) is a Mexican politician from the Party of the Democratic Revolution. From 2006 to 2009 she served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Morelos. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:People from Morelos Category:Women members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Party of the Democratic Revolution politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:21st-century Mexican women politicians
